extends layout.pug

block content
  h2 Your Appointment is Confirmed

  p Dear #{userName},

  p Thank you for booking an appointment with Glow Cosmetics. We're delighted to confirm your upcoming service.

  .appointment-box(style='background-color: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;')
    table(style='width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;')
      tr
        td(style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;') Service:
        td(style='padding: 8px 0;') #{serviceName}
      tr
        td(style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;') Date:
        td(style='padding: 8px 0;') #{appointmentDate}
      tr
        td(style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;') Time:
        td(style='padding: 8px 0;') #{appointmentTime}
      tr
        td(style='padding: 8px 0; font-weight: bold;') Booking Reference:
        td(style='padding: 8px 0;') #{bookingId}

  p We look forward to welcoming you to our salon. Please arrive 10 minutes before your appointment time to ensure a seamless experience.

  if specialInstructions
    .instructions-box(style='margin: 24px 0; padding: 16px; background-color: #f0f7ff; border-left: 4px solid var(--primary); border-radius: 4px;')
      h4(style='margin-top: 0;') Special Instructions
      p #{specialInstructions}

  p(style='margin: 24px 0;')
    a(
      href=rescheduleUrl,
      target='_blank',
      rel='noopener noreferrer',
      style='display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 500;'
    ) Reschedule Appointment

  .divider

  h4 Appointment Policies

  ul(style='list-style: none; padding-left: 0;')
    li(style='padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;')
      strong Cancellation Policy:
      br
      | Please provide at least 24 hours notice for cancellations to avoid a cancellation fee.
    li(style='padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;')
      strong Late Arrival:
      br
      | If you arrive late, your service may be shortened to accommodate other scheduled appointments.

  p If you need to reschedule or have any questions, please contact us at (123) 456-7890.

  p
    strong Glow Cosmetics Team